					<p class="text-sm text-light">That need to scale operations without exponentially increasing headcount.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="text-center p-6 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-b from-special-lighter to-transparent border border-special-light">
					<div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-accent-base/10 flex items-center justify-center">
						<Icon name="mdi:office-building" class="w-8 h-8 text-accent-base" />
					</div>
					<h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Established companies</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-light">Looking to modernize processes and adopt AI strategically.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="text-center p-6 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-b from-special-lighter to-transparent border border-special-light">
					<div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-accent-base/10 flex items-center justify-center">
						<Icon name="mdi:account-multiple" class="w-8 h-8 text-accent-base" />
					</div>
					<h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Specific teams</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-light">Operations, marketing, sales, finance or IT teams looking to automate their area.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Pricing Section -->
		<section class="mb-16">
			<h2>Investment</h2>
